  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0dba\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dcf\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db1 \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad \u0dc1\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A Hyundai vehicle assembly factory to Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Hyundai Motor Company, the world's sixth largest car manufacturer, has entered into an agreement with Abans Auto for assembly in Sri Lanka.",
        "Thus, Abans Auto Company has received permission to assemble and manufacture Hyundai cars and accessories in Sri Lanka.",
        "Hyundai is a car manufacturer in Korea and Abans Auto Company is the authorized distributor of these cars in Sri Lanka.",
        "This agreement has been signed as a result of a long discussion started in 2020 for the assembly of those cars in Sri Lanka.",
        "Hyundai has extensive experience in setting up automobile assembly plants around the world and currently operates in eight countries, including the United States, the Czech Republic and India.",
        "Similarly, the proposed assembly plant for Sri Lanka has been designed by Hyundai and will include modern technologies, tools and equipment that are in line with Industry 4.0 standards, ensuring that the brand's stringent quality expectations are maintained.",
        "Some components needed to assemble these cars are also going to be manufactured in Sri Lanka."
      ],
